text: Ronja Steinborn (born 23 December 1990) is a German modern pentathlete. She participated at the 2018 World Modern Pentathlon Championships, winning a medal.Relay results ==References== ==External links== * Category:Living people Category:1990 births Category:German female modern pentathletes Category:World Modern Pentathlon Championships medalists Category:Sportspeople from Berlin
